profile:
Invisible Windows Inc. is the proud winner of the Consumer Choice Award 7th year in a row for window cleaning Southern Alberta. We have been providing window cleaning services, eavestrough/gutter cleaning, and pressure washing for residential homes and to over 400 businesses on a regular basis in Calgary and area since 2008, including property managers, home builders, and cleaning businesses. We do everything from storefront route work, post construction cleans to high rise buildings and customer satisfaction is a priority on all our projects. 
We provide these services not just in Calgary but also surrounding areas, including Airdrie, Okotoks, Chestermere, and Cochrane. 

We can clean your windows inside or out, bi-weekly, monthly, quarterly, or whatever fits your schedule. We pride ourselves on being prompt, courteous, and professional at your residential or commercial place. Friendly, fully trained and insured employees will arrive to provide top quality service specific to your needs.
